  ('dietitian-moex-11047', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是管理者為員工工作內容說明書擬定必須注意之原則？ 工作目標需符合該員工之需求  規定的工作表現標準是可達成的 工作表現標準是可觀察或是可測量的  工作內容明確', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11048', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '蛋加水於高溫下烹煮，成品呈多孔狀，是產生什麼作用或現象？ 燒焦（Coagulation）現象    起泡（Foaming Ability）作用 乳化（Emulsification）作用   離水（Syneresis）現象', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11049', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據勞動基準法的規定，雇主依規定終止勞動契約者，其預告期間依規定應為： 繼續工作三個月以上一年未滿者，於五日前預告之  繼續工作三個月以上一年未滿者，於十日前預告之 繼續工作三個月以上一年未滿者，於十五日前預告之  繼續工作三個月以上一年未滿者，於二十日前預告之', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11050', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據勞動基準法的規定，以下那一項是正確的？ 在同一雇主之事業單位繼續工作，每滿一年發給相當於一個月平均工資之資遣費 在同一雇主之事業單位繼續工作，每滿一年發給相當於二個月平均工資之資遣費 在同一雇主之事業單位繼續工作，每滿一年發給相當於三個月平均工資之資遣費 在同一雇主之事業單位繼續工作，每滿一年發給相當於四個月平均工資之資遣費', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0d2b7b701024", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b75a8902103e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
